 \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{{(n+3)!} (4^n)}{{5n}^{n+2}}  
 \lim_{n=\infty} \frac{{(n+3+1)!} (4^{n+1})}{{(5n+1)}^{n+2+1}} . \frac{{(5n)}^{n+2}} {{(n+3)!} (4^{n})} 
a_n=\frac{(n+3)!4^n}{5n^{n+2}}
\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}a_{n+1}/a_n
 \log\frac{{(n+3)!} (4^n)}{{5n}^{n+2}} = \log (n+3)! + n\log 4 - (n+2)\log n - \log 5 \\=\ (n+3)\log (n+3) - (n+3) + n\log 4 - (n+2)\log n+ O(\log n)\\ =  n(\log 4-1) + O(\log n)\to\infty 
